textAnnotations.description:
After a long wait a bus appeared and they
followed the beaming Dan aboard, taking
seats some rows behind him. Here was
beginning to find the sterechpped, fluttish, happy
faces very dinoncerking; and looking at
Heather he found a welcome reliet in her
relatively long dolekul one
